<ContentLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Abelost handles calculator inputs, analytics, advertising, cookies, and contact information." eyebrow="Last updated June 9, 2026">
  <h2>Calculator inputs</h2>
  <p>Calculator values are processed locally in your browser. Abelost does not intentionally transmit or store the numbers you enter into calculator fields.</p>
  <h2>Technical logs</h2>
  <p>Our hosting provider may process standard request information such as IP address, browser type, requested URL, timestamps, and security signals to deliver the site, prevent abuse, and diagnose errors.</p>
  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>We may use privacy-conscious analytics to understand aggregate page usage and site performance. If analytics requiring consent are introduced, the site will provide the legally appropriate notice and controls.</p>
  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>We may display advertising supplied by Google or other partners. Advertising providers may use cookies or similar technologies to deliver, measure, and personalize ads where permitted. Consent controls will be shown where required. You can review Google's information about how it uses data on partner sites at <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites">policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites</a>.</p>
  <h2>Contact messages</h2>
  <p>If you email us, we receive the address and information you provide. We use it to respond, investigate issues, and maintain reasonable business records.</p>
  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <p>You can block or delete cookies using your browser settings. Depending on your location, you may have rights to request access, correction, deletion, or restriction of personal information. Contact <a href="mailto:privacy@abelost.com">privacy@abelost.com</a>.</p>
  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy as the site and applicable requirements change. The revision date at the top identifies the current version.</p>
</ContentLayout>
